---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  pageId="privacy"
  title="Privacy Policy • GreenEdge"
  description="Learn how GreenEdge collects, uses, and protects your personal information across the platform and APIs."
>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="page-nav">
        <a class="nav-brand" href="/">GreenEdge</a>
        <a href="/">← Back to home</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main-content" class="legal">
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Effective date: August 22, 2024</p>
        <p>
          GreenEdge respects your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and the choices you
          have when interacting with our Services.
        </p>

        <h2>Information we collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Account details:</strong> Names, email addresses, and age verification records submitted during onboarding.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Page views, feature interactions, and accessibility preferences captured via Plausible and PostHog.</li>
          <li><strong>Content submissions:</strong> Reviews, reservations, and strain data you submit through our serverless APIs.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How we use information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Operate, maintain, and improve the Services and underlying infrastructure.</li>
          <li>Personalize experiences such as strain recommendations and reservation confirmations.</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations, including cannabis industry regulations and community standards.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data sharing</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell your personal information. Limited data may be shared with trusted vendors that provide hosting, analytics,
          or compliance services, each bound by confidentiality agreements.
        </p>

        <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
        <p>
          GreenEdge uses privacy-focused analytics with cookieless tracking whenever possible. Where cookies are required, we ask
          for consent and honor regional privacy laws including GDPR and CCPA.
        </p>

        <h2>Your choices</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Update or delete your account by emailing <a href="mailto:privacy@greenedge.nyc">privacy@greenedge.nyc</a>.</li>
          <li>Opt out of marketing communications via the unsubscribe links in our emails.</li>
          <li>Adjust analytics preferences within your account dashboard.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your information, including TLS encryption,
          role-based access controls, and continuous monitoring.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy periodically. Significant updates will be announced on the site and through email when applicable.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Reach out to <a href="mailto:privacy@greenedge.nyc">privacy@greenedge.nyc</a> with privacy questions or concerns.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
